What do you find in here?

File moepbot.php is the starter for the bot. You need a configfile as provided
with moepbot.cfg. Start the bot with:

   $ ./moepbot.php -c moepbot.cfg


Directory moepbot/classes contains all the classes about the MoepBot. 
The classes are:

    MoepIrc     - handles all the basic network and irc-protocol stuff
    MoepBot     - extends MoepIrc and handles the bot basic functionality
    MoepEvent   - describes a incoming irc-event
    MoepUtil    - collects tools for common use
    MoepScript  - realises scripting (scripts may be changed while runtime)
    ...
